---
title: Pork Schnitzel & Katsu Sauce with Rapid Rice & Creamy Bacon Slaw
description: Warm, tart and sweet - all words we use to describe luscious katsu sauce, the superhero sidekick of Japanese cuisine! Pour it over a golden crumbed pork schnitzel with fluffy rice, and watch as every bite becomes a delicious thrill ride.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6633376964b58f12a733fb04-f4107605.jpeg
